item.title: JAZZ SPECIAL STOMPRADIO.COM 2009
item.description: WORDS TOO FOLLOW...... http://funky-soul-vinyls.blogspot.com http://www.back2backfm.net back with another archive show, something i found on a sunny day in london chilling in the garden needing to feed a jazz taste i had with my cornflakes!!!!!!!!. one with the old chief lloyd @ bathworks http:// www.bath-works.co.uk in woodford in mind bringing back memories of the jazz room at caister.May have posted this b4 but hey....the musics baaaaaad just ignore me talking bolloxs all over it..dont forget to check out the two links above back2back really kicking arse in london right now and just to prove there are still some nice guys left in the dj world.thanx again to everyone who downloads subscribes streams edits nicks this podast !!! do what ever you want with its youres i only link the the music up the talented ones have produced and played the tracks.......till nxt time as they say........keep ya tongue out.............sorry forgot welcome to the phillipines and barbados to this podcast now downloaded in 59 countries.love you all ..nathan blake

item.title: FROM LONDON TO PARIS
item.description: PROBABLY THE FIRST NEW COMPILATION IVE DONE FOR A WHILE, ANYONE WHOS LISTENED, DOWNLOADED ANY OF MY PODCASTS BEING MIXES OR ARCHIVE SHOWS OVER THE LAST COUPLE OF YEARS WOULD KNOW IM A BIT OF A DISCO"ITE".LOTS MAY NOT AGREE BUT I SEE HOUSE MUSIC AS A CONTINUATION OF THE GLITTER BALL DAYS OF THE SEVENTIES. I ALSO BELIEVE IN MOVING MUSIC FWD, I LOVE RE MAKES OF CLASSICS, TWO OF THE "GUVNORS"BEING JOEY NEGRO AND MR PANAM HIMSELF DIMITRI FROM PARIS...SO HERES A LITTLE COMPILATION OF DIMITRI FROM PARIS RE EDITS WITH OFCOURSE SOME TONGUE IN CHEEK NB JINGLES THROWN OVER THE TOP. THANX TO FUNKY SOUL VINYLS BLOG FOR FEATURING 2 OF MY LATEST OFFERINGS http://funky-soul-vinyls.blogspot.com http://www.back2backfm.net/ ON PUBLISHING THIS PODCAST WE NEAR THE TENTH ANNIVERSARY OF DEATH OF NEARLY 3000 PEOPLE IN THE TWIN TOWERS.....231 FIREFIGHTERS.........10 PARAMEDICS............WHY? MY THOUGHTS GO OUT AT THIS TIME TO THE MANY PEOPLE WHO HAVE LOST AS A CONSEQUENCE OF THIS MURDEROUS ACTION ON 9/11....THINKING OF YOU ACROSS THE POND......... HERES THE TRACKLISTING ENJOY THE BEATS...NATHAN BLAKE SATURDAY..........NORMA JEAN WRIGHT HURT SO BAD.......PHILLY DEVOTIONS BAD LUCK..........HAROLD MELVYNAND THE BLUE NOTES THE NIGHT THE LIGHTS WENT OUT......THE TRAMPS RICHIE FAMILY.....FRENESI YOU CANT HIDE FROM YOURESELF.......TEDDY P ALL TRACKS RE EDITED BY DIMITRI FROM PARIS AND CUT TOGETHER BY NATHAN BLAKE

item.title: NATHAN BLAKE GOES BANANAS
item.description: HERE SOMETHING I FOUND IN MY TAPE BOX UP IN THE LOFT, CASSETTE I BOUGHT FROM A CLUB 1986 ISH RECORDED LIVE FROM A CLUB CALLED BANANAS IN TENERIFE,NO CDS OR COMPUTER PROGRAMES THIS WAS THE OLD WAY SL1200,S OR 1210,S IF YOU LIKE, TOWARDS THE END OF THE TAPE YOU WILL DISCOVER THE BEGINING OF WHAT WE NOW KNOW AS "HOUSE MUSIC" ENJOY THE MIX ITS WHAT IM LISTENING TO AT THE MOMENT..................NATHAN BLAKE http://funky-soul-vinyls.blogspot.com http://www.back2backfm.net/
